::Food Result [Important/Needed nobr]
/*
RESULT OF EACH FOOD CARD.
Tells the player whether they were right and explains why.
Moves to next round or meal builder after round 6.
*/

<div class="phone">
<div class="header"><span>DASH Game</span><span class="round-label">Round $round of 6</span></div>

<div class="meters-wrap">
<div class="meter-row"><div class="meter-label">Correct</div><div class="meter-bar"><div class="meter-bar-fill correct" @style="'width: ' + Math.min(100, ($score / 6) * 100) + '%'"></div></div></div>
<div class="meter-row"><div class="meter-label">Wrong</div><div class="meter-bar"><div class="meter-bar-fill wrong" @style="'width: ' + Math.min(100, ($wrong / 6) * 100) + '%'"></div></div></div>
</div>

<div class="content">

<div class="result-card">
<<if $lastFood is "banana">><span class="result-emoji">🍌</span><<elseif $lastFood is "noodles">><span class="result-emoji">🍜</span><<elseif $lastFood is "darkchocolate">><span class="result-emoji">🍫</span><<elseif $lastFood is "bacon">><span class="result-emoji">🥓</span><<elseif $lastFood is "spinach">><span class="result-emoji">🥬</span><<else>><span class="result-emoji">🥫</span><</if>>

<<if $lastCorrect is true>><div class="result-verdict correct">Correct</div><<else>><div class="result-verdict wrong">Not quite</div><</if>>

<p class="result-explain"><<if $lastFood is "banana">>Bananas are high in potassium, which helps your kidneys flush excess sodium out. Less sodium means less pressure on your artery walls. A banana a day is a real cardiovascular tool.<<elseif $lastFood is "noodles">>One packet of instant noodles can contain 1500 milligrams of sodium. The recommended daily limit is 2300. One packet gets you halfway there before anything else.<<elseif $lastFood is "darkchocolate">>Dark chocolate contains flavonoids that help blood vessels relax and widen. A small amount, around one square, can produce a measurable drop in blood pressure. The key word is small.<<elseif $lastFood is "bacon">>Bacon is cured in salt and high in saturated fat. Sodium increases blood volume. Saturated fat stiffens artery walls. Together they are a real cardiovascular load.<<elseif $lastFood is "spinach">>Spinach is high in potassium and magnesium, two minerals that directly support healthy blood pressure. One of the most nutrient-dense foods for the heart.<<else>>One serving of canned soup often contains 800 to 1200 milligrams of sodium. Many cans hold two servings. Checking labels on canned food is one of the best things you can do for blood pressure.<</if>></p>
</div>

<<if $round lt 6>>
<<set $round to $round + 1>>
<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Round Start">NEXT FOOD</a>
<a class="btn-secondary" data-passage="Central Hub">BACK TO CARDIOCAREQUEST</a>
<<else>>
<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Meal Builder Intro">NOW BUILD A MEAL</a>
<<set $round to $round + 1>>
<</if>>

</div>
</div>


::Meal Builder Intro [Important/Needed nobr]
/*
TRANSITION: Cards done. Introduce meal building.
*/

<div class="phone">
<div class="header"><span>DASH Game</span><span class="round-label">Part 2</span></div>
<div class="content">

<span class="hero-emoji">🍽️</span>

<h2 class="intro-title">Build a Meal</h2>

<p class="narrative center">You scored $score out of 6 on the cards.</p>

<p class="narrative">Now pick ingredients to build a meal. Tap each one to add it. The score bar fills as you choose.</p>

<p class="narrative">No wrong answers here. The point is to see what each choice does.</p>

<div class="spacer"></div>

<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Meal Builder">START BUILDING</a>

</div>
</div>


::Meal Builder [Important/Needed nobr]
/*
MEAL BUILDER: Player picks ingredients.
Each <<linkreplace>> can be triggered once.
Score bar reflects $mealScore.
*/

<div class="phone">
<div class="header"><span>DASH Game</span><span class="round-label">Build a meal</span></div>

<div class="score-bar-wrap">
<span class="score-label">Meal score</span>
<div class="score-bar"><div class="score-bar-fill" @style="'width: ' + Math.max(0, Math.min(100, ($mealScore + 50))) + '%'"></div></div>
</div>

<div class="content">

<div class="section-label">Proteins</div>
<div class="ingredients-grid">
<span id="ing01" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🍚</span><span class="ing-name">Brown rice</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🍚 Brown rice"), State.variables.mealScore += 10, $("#ing01").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🍚</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span><span id="ing02" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🍲</span><span class="ing-name">Beans</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🍲 Beans"), State.variables.mealScore += 15, $("#ing02").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🍲</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span><span id="ing03" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🥓</span><span class="ing-name">Bacon</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🥓 Bacon"), State.variables.mealScore -= 15, $("#ing03").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🥓</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span><span id="ing04" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🥛</span><span class="ing-name">Yogurt</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🥛 Yogurt"), State.variables.mealScore += 10, $("#ing04").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🥛</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span>
</div>

<div class="section-label">Vegetables and Fruit</div>
<div class="ingredients-grid">
<span id="ing05" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🥬</span><span class="ing-name">Spinach</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🥬 Spinach"), State.variables.mealScore += 15, $("#ing05").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🥬</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span><span id="ing06" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🍅</span><span class="ing-name">Tomato</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🍅 Tomato"), State.variables.mealScore += 10, $("#ing06").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🍅</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span><span id="ing07" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🍌</span><span class="ing-name">Banana</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🍌 Banana"), State.variables.mealScore += 10, $("#ing07").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🍌</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span><span id="ing08" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🍟</span><span class="ing-name">Potato chips</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🍟 Potato chips"), State.variables.mealScore -= 10, $("#ing08").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🍟</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span>
</div>

<div class="section-label">Extras</div>
<div class="ingredients-grid">
<span id="ing09" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🍫</span><span class="ing-name">Dark chocolate</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🍫 Dark chocolate"), State.variables.mealScore += 5, $("#ing09").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🍫</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span><span id="ing10" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🍜</span><span class="ing-name">Instant noodles</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🍜 Instant noodles"), State.variables.mealScore -= 20, $("#ing10").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🍜</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span><span id="ing11" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">💧</span><span class="ing-name">Water</span>'>><<run $meal.push("💧 Water"), State.variables.mealScore += 5, $("#ing11").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">💧</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span><span id="ing12" class="ing-wrap"><<linkreplace '<span class="ing-emoji">🌭</span><span class="ing-name">Hot dog</span>'>><<run $meal.push("🌭 Hot dog"), State.variables.mealScore -= 15, $("#ing12").addClass("selected")>><span class="ing-emoji">🌭</span><span class="ing-name added-name">✓ Added</span><</linkreplace>></span>
</div>

<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Meal Result">SEE MY MEAL RESULT</a>

</div>
</div>


::Meal Result [Important/Needed nobr]
/*
MEAL RESULT: Shows what meal does to BP.
Personalized message based on $mealScore.
Lists what player picked.
*/

<div class="phone">
<div class="header"><span>DASH Game</span><span class="round-label">Your meal</span></div>

<div class="score-bar-wrap">
<span class="score-label">Meal score</span>
<div class="score-bar"><div class="score-bar-fill" @style="'width: ' + Math.max(0, Math.min(100, ($mealScore + 50))) + '%'"></div></div>
</div>

<div class="content">

<div class="meal-list-card">
<<if $meal.length gt 0>><div class="meal-emojis"><<for _item range $meal>><<print _item.split(" ")[0]>> <</for>></div><</if>>

<<if $mealScore gte 30>>
<div class="meal-verdict strong">Strong DASH meal</div>
<p class="meal-explain">Your ingredient choices are high in potassium, fiber, and minerals that actively support lower blood pressure. A meal like this, eaten regularly, produces measurable results over weeks.</p>
<<elseif $mealScore gte 10>>
<div class="meal-verdict moderate">Moderate DASH meal</div>
<p class="meal-explain">Some strong choices in there. Swapping one high-sodium ingredient for a potassium-rich one would shift this meal a lot in the right direction.</p>
<<elseif $mealScore gte 0>>
<div class="meal-verdict mixed">Mixed meal</div>
<p class="meal-explain">The DASH-friendly choices are being offset by the high-sodium ones. Small swaps make a real difference here.</p>
<<else>>
<div class="meal-verdict weak">Working against you</div>
<p class="meal-explain">This meal is working against your blood pressure. The sodium load is high and the potassium is low. Try replacing one ingredient and see what changes.</p>
<</if>>
</div>

<div class="spacer"></div>

<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Story innit">PLAY AGAIN</a>
<a class="btn-secondary" data-passage="Central Hub">BACK TO CARDIOCAREQUEST</a>

</div>
</div>


::Central Hub [Important/Needed nobr]
/*
Placeholder. In the full app this returns to CardioCareQuest hub.
*/

<div class="phone">
<div class="header"><span>DASH Game</span></div>
<div class="content">

<span class="hero-emoji">🏠</span>

<h2 class="intro-title">Returning</h2>

<p class="narrative center">Returning to CardioCareQuest.</p>

<div class="spacer"></div>

<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Story innit">PLAY DASH GAME AGAIN</a>

</div>
</div>
